headline: Kroger Chief People Officer Tim Massa Inducted as a Fellow of the National Academy of Human Resources
summary: The Kroger Co. (NYSE: KR) today announced Kroger's senior vice president and chief people officer Tim Massa's induction to the National Academy of Human Resources (NAHR) as a fellow. NAHR fellows are recognized for their sustained achievements and contributions to their organizations, the HR profession and society at large.
